<body>

    <h1>caffe d'orzo</h1>
    <p>A tempestuous morning
Making bitter milk
Coffee is Overrated</p>

    <h2>boundless</h2>
    <p>Glad I trekked miles abundant 
Across time and space.     
It brought me into your arms</p>

    <h3>picture frame</h3>
    <p>An empty picture frame sits
Anticipating
For a tender memory</p>

